# 2p_legs — host. Spawns next to client and walks left/right
# repeatedly at close range. Pairs with 2p_legs.client.shot.
# Verifies the host mech's leg-swing animation is visible in
# the client's view (regression test for the snapshot anim_id
# bug where the client always saw remote mechs as ANIM_STAND
# regardless of motion → mechs slid instead of walked).

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/legs_host
network host 24091
name HostA

spawn_at 2300 1112
peer_spawn 1 2400 1112

aim 2400 1080

# Walk back and forth several times. Each press should produce
# clear leg-swing animation visible from the client's view.
at 100 press right
at 180 release right
at 200 press left
at 320 release left
at 340 press right
at 460 release right
at 480 press left
at 580 release left

at 140 shot t140_running_right
at 260 shot t260_running_left
at 400 shot t400_running_right
at 520 shot t520_running_left
at 650 shot t650_stopped
at 750 end
